text: Old Trafford is a football stadium in Trafford. Its nickname is Theatre of Dreams". It is home to the club Manchester United F.C.. It is a club stadium in Great Britain. Old Trafford hosted most of England's home matches while Wembley was being built. It was built in 1910. It cost about Â£60,000,000 to build.
